The paper deals with image similarity and uses deep siamese networks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of curriculum learning is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of multi-scale CNNs, which are used in multimedia processing (cs.MM). The task of fetching similar images is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and the use of deep learning techniques falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
